<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background: #4a90e2; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; }
    .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #888; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background: #4a90e2; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h2>Request Approved!</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{studentName}},</p>
      <p>Great news! Your request for the course <strong>{{courseSubject}}</strong> has been approved by <strong>{{tutorName}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>Your 48-hour trial period starts now and will end on <strong>{{trialEndDate}}</strong>.</p>
      <p>During the trial period, you can chat with the tutor to discuss your requirements. Note that file and image sharing are disabled until payment is complete.</p>
      <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Thank you for using TutorFinder!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
